OL,3,CJersey school children to explore
OL,4,Cclimate change through art
OL,6,FA new project by ArtHouse Jersey will
OL,7,Fencourage local school children to
OL,8,Fexplore climate change through art and
OL,9,Fdesign.
OL,11,FThe 'Gem of the Sea' was the result of
OL,12,Fa review instigated by the COP26
OL,13,F'Education Pledge' which found young
OL,14,Fpeople in Jersey want to understand
OL,15,Fhow climate change will impact the
OL,16,Ffuture of their island home.
OL,18,FArtHouse Jersey will provide digital
OL,19,Fresources for schools across the
OL,20,Fisland to deliver art lessons
OL,21,Fexploring various themes, including:
