OL,6,FSix digital 'episodes' will be made
OL,7,Favailable free of charge to Jersey
OL,8,Fteachers, which aim to help children
OL,9,Fexplore these global problems from a
OL,10,Flocal perspective.
OL,12,FThey will also offer opportunities to
OL,13,Freinforce other curriculum areas such
OL,14,Fas oracy, science, geography, and PSHE.
OL,16,FThe title of the project is inspired
OL,17,Fby lyrics from Jersey's patriotic song
OL,18,F'Beautiful Jersey', and a special
OL,19,Fepisode will also be released to
OL,20,Fcommemorate the 80th anniversary of
OL,21,Fthe Liberation.
