OL,3,CJersey school children to explore
OL,4,Cclimate change through art
OL,6,FKate Sugden, curriculum advisor to the
OL,7,Fproject, says it will give children a
OL,8,Fchance to respond to the potential
OL,9,Fchallenges their future holds in a
OL,10,Fcreative way.
OL,12,FShe says: "Driven by the voices of our
OL,13,Fchildren and young people across the
OL,14,Feducation sector, this initiative
OL,15,Fmodernises the art and design
OL,16,Fcurriculum to reflect the local and
OL,17,Fglobal context, fostering a generation
OL,18,Fthat is prepared to lead with
OL,19,Fimagination, resilience, and a deep
OL,20,Fsense of community."
